section#register.register
  h4.header-section.header-section--secondary register & pricing
  .col-50-s
    h5.section__subject.header-subject Join conference
    h6.section__caption.header-caption-alt London conference
    .section__text.section__text--s
      p.p.p--common-alt Sed vitae tincidunt ante, vel lacinia odio. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Morbi feugiat nisi nec ex convallis fringilla. Cras sit amet fermentum elit. Sed fermentum sollicitudin neque, ut pulvinar erat lobortis a. Maecenas facilisis, lectus a convallis volutpat, nisi est tristique ante, eget tempus nisl neque at arcu.
    .section__contacts
      a.link-common(href="mailto:someone@email.com") 
        strong kanew.doe
        | @conference.co
      +social
  .col-50-s
    form#form-register.register__form(action="register.php" method="post")
      input.input(name="register-name" placeholder="Name & Surname")
      input.form__element.input(name="register-email" placeholder="Email Address")
      input.form__element.input(name="register-phone" placeholder="Phone Number")
      .select-wrapper.form__element
        select(name="register-plan")
          option(disabled selected) Select your plan...
          option(value="personal") $ 101 - Personal
          option(value="business") $ 114 - Business
          option(value="company") $ 120 - Company
      button.form__element.btn-join(type="submit") Join the 
        strong Conference
        svg
          use(xlink:href="img/design/sprite.svg#icon-arrow-right")
